 vṛṣasārasaṃgrahaḥ 

\par*** 1 ***\par
 prathamo 'dhyāyaḥ 

\par\par anādimadhyāntam anantapāraṃ

        \footnote{1a <LEM>°ntam ananta°</LEM> \msCa\msCbpcorr\msCc\msNa\msNb\msNc\Ed; °ntam anta° \msCbacorr\oo

