                                   sarvakāmika \msCc, sārvakālikaḥ \msNa, sārvakāmikāḥ \msNb}

         \footnote{5ab Ł See a sequence or list of the four āśramas in 4.57: $

                gṛhastho brahmacārī ca vānaprastho 'tha bhaikṣukaḥ;

