                etac chaucaṃ gṛhasthānāṃ dviguṇaṃ brahmacāriṇām|

                vānaprasthasya triguṇaṃ yatīnāṃ tu caturguṇam||</PARAL>

\par akṣayaś cāvyayaś caiva sarvapātakanāśanaḥ||11.5||

        \footnote{5c <LEM>akṣayaś cāvyayaś</LEM> \msCb\msNb\msNc\Ed; akṣayaṃ cāvyayaṃ \msCa\msCc\msNa}

