\par*** 22 ***\par
 22 varṇagotrāśramaḥ 

\par janamejaya uvāca| 

\par śruto 'thābjamukhād dharmasārasaṃgraham uttamam|

        \footnote{Gender problem or śruto = I heard.}

        \footnote{1a <LEM>śruto 'thābjamukhād dharma°</LEM> \eme; 

        śruto vābjamukhād dharmaḥ \msCa, śruto vābjamukhod dharmaḥ \msCb, śruto vābjamukhā dharmaḥ \msCc, 

        śruto cābjamukhād dharmaḥ \msNa\msL, śruto cābdamukhā dharmaḥ \msNb, śrutvā vābjamukhād dharmaḥ \msNc,

                        śruto vā tvanmukhād dharmaḥ \Ed}

        <PARAL>ŁTestimonia for this chapter: \msCa\ ff. 232r--234v, \msCb\ ff. 233v--235r, \msCc\ ff. 314r--317r,

                \msNa\ ff. 39r--41v, \msNb\ ff. 241v--243v, \msNc\ ff. 247v--250r;

                C = \msCa + \msCb + \msCc $</PARAL>

