\par daśayajñavrataṃ cīrṇaṃ daśakāmaparājitaḥ|

        \footnote{11a <LEM>daśayajñavrataṃ cīrṇaṃ</LEM> \msNa\msNb\msNc\msL; da\uncl{śayajñaṃ} ××ñ cīrṇan \msCa, 

